- Network file system that can be mounted on 100s of Ec2
- EFS work with Linuz EC2 instances in Multi-AZ
- Highly available, scalable, expensive , pay-per-use.

- EFS infrequent access (EFS-IA)
    - Storage class that is cost-optimized for files that are not accessed every day.
    - Up to 92% lower cost compared to EFS Standard.
    - EFS will automatically move your files to EFS-IA based on the last time they were accessed.
    - Define policy and move to IA after e.g 60 days not accessed.
    - Transparent cost optimization.